<Layout title="How Brisbane City Plan Amendments and TLPIs Affect Property Sale Value | Daniel Gierach Property" description="Brisbane City Plan amendments and Temporary Local Planning Instruments can move sale value before they are even gazetted. How planning changes flow through to price, what to verify, and how to time a campaign around a pending change." schema={faqSchema}>

<article style="background:var(--color-surface-0);min-height:100vh;">

  <!-- Hero -->
